<p id="fs-idm19598048">The fraction of <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow>

<msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>27</mn></mrow><mn>60</mn></msubsup><mtext>Co</mtext>

</mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow>

