</mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow>

<msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.5em"/><mn>94</mn></mrow><mn>245</mn></msubsup><mtext>Pu</mtext>

</mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
</div><div data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp54341232"><div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp90959696">
<p id="fs-idm5650336">The following nuclei do not lie in the band of stability. How would they be expected to decay?</p>
<p id="fs-idp92587472">(a) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow>

